Dialogs.Text: Thomas B: None of those two seemed to be my contact.
Thomas B: ...That means i have to figure out the message i received on my own.
Thomas B: And also means that i'm probably not the only one looking for that.
Thomas B: Now that nobody is here, i think i have something i can use somewhere.
Thomas B: If that doesn't work, i guess i should call it a day.
Thomas B: I have one of the things the message said, now i have to know where to use it. (Portraits pendant)
